6&amp;pmid=24598442">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">12.</div><div id="r12" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Schnell S, Ansari SA, Wu C, et al. Accelerated dual-venc 4D flow MRI for neurovascular applications. <em>J Magn Reson Imaging</em> 2017;46(1):102–114.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1002/jmri.25595">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/28152256/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Accelerated+dual-venc+4D+flow+MRI+for+neurovascular+applications&amp;author=S+Schnell&amp;author=SA+Ansari&amp;author=C+Wu&amp;publication_year=2017&amp;journal=J+Magn+Reson+Imaging&amp;pages=102-114&amp;doi=10.1002%2Fjmri.25595&amp;pmid=28152256">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">13.</div><div id="r13" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Buonocore MH. Visualizing blood flow patterns using streamlines, arrows, and particle paths. <em>Magn Reson Med</em> 1998;40(2):210–226.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1002/mrm.1910400207">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/9702703/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Visualizing+blood+flow+patterns+using+streamlines%2C+arrows%2C+and+particle+paths&amp;author=MH+Buonocore&amp;publication_year=1998&amp;journal=Magn+Reson+Med&amp;pages=210-226&amp;doi=10.1002%2Fmrm.1910400207&amp;pmid=9702703">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">14.</div><div id="r14" class="citations"><div class="citation">